# ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
# iNStab-cart                                              #
# ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
#   FEM f90 code for stability and response analysis for   #
#   INCOMPRESSIBLE fluids. This is the cartesian version   #
#   of the code for 2d - 2v flows                          #
# ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
#
# 1. Analyses: +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
#    1- Steady Solution
#    2- Eigenproblem
#     - ...
#     - ...
#    _- Centre Manifold Reduction
#    _- Harmonic Gain Analysis
#    _- Stochastic Gain Analysis
#    _- Sensitivity Analysis
#
# 2. Libraries: ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
#    Several libraries are required: please check Makefile
#    ...
#
# 3. TODOs +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ #
#    This is a beta version. Some of the required checks
#    are listed below: 
#    - -fcheck=all (-fcheck=bounds) introduces error in
#      the HG analysis.
#    - Centre Manifold Reduction is written for bif with
#      cod .GE. 1, but interaction of perturbations with
#      different wavenumber must be implemented yet.
#    - ...

